title: CTA CHEST ABDOMEN PELVIS WITH CONTRAST

technique.description: CT images of the cervical spine read without intravenous contrast.

findings.bones: Normal vertebral alignment. Normal vertebral body height. No acute fracture. Densis intact, C1 and C2 are normally aligned, and the atlantodental interval is normal.
findings.spinal: No osseous narrowing of the spinal canal
findings.soft: No prevertebral soft tissue swelling. Visualized neck soft tissues are normal.
